quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,7,"∆Āen …ďe jortaaki hawrugol e Amen, …ďe weltori nguurndam aduna …óam, …ďe dee∆īiri …óam, e …ďen taw…ďe no welsindii e Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  10,8,"∆Āen, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Yiite ngen, sabu kon ko faggittonoo"
  10,9,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, Joomi ma…ď…ďe feewnay…ďe e gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Can…ói no ila ley ma…ď…ďe ka Aljannaaji neema"
  10,10,"Noddaandu ma…ď…ďe nder ton, ko \"Ya Alla senaade woodaniima\", hiwrondiral ma…ď…ďe ngal ton, ko : \"Salaam\", [kisal]. Ko woni wattannde noddaandu ma…ď…ďe, ko : \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, Jey…óo Winndere nden"
  10,11,"Sinno Alla yaccinanayno yim…ďe …ďen bone wano O yacciniranta …ďe mo∆ī∆īere, lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal timminanteno …ďe. Men acca …ďen …ďe tam∆īinaaki hawrugol e Amen e bewre ma…ď…ďe nden hi…ďe bumam-bumannoo"
  10,12,"Si lorra memii ne…ó…óanke on, o nodda men …ďaŇčŇče makko, maa ko joo…óii…óo, maa ko o darii…óo. Tuma nde Men huncini mo lorra makko kan, o fe∆ī∆īira wa si o noddaano Men e lorra memuka mo. Ko wano non fantinoo…ďe …ďen cu…óiranaa kon ko …ďe gollaynoo"
  10,13,"Gom…óii Men halkiino gire adinoo…ďe on nde …ďe too√Īunoo, Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. ∆Āe wonaano gom…óinoo…ďe. Ko wana nii Men yo…ďirta yim…ďe bom…ďe …ďen"
  10,14,"Refti Men Men wa…ói on lontotoo…ďe ka leydi …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, ha min ndaara no gollirton"
